room_title: Escape room "The Awakening" by Time to Escape in Okeechobee
room_description:
There is always more than meets the eye and The Awakening is no exception to that rule. Detective JW Warren has been missing for weeks. Strange things have been happening and it seems to have gotten a lot worse since JW has disappeared...
There is a disease that has broken out and you fear for his safety. You will search the Detective's Office for clues to these strange disappearances, including the Detective himself. Since his departure, there have been rumors of experimentation and an elusive cure. It is up to you to uncover it all!
